Class RecreationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epam.recreation_module.controller.RecreationController

  • @RestController
 @RequestMapping(value="/recreation")
 @CrossOrigin
public class RecreationController
extends java.lang.Object
    Class CommentaryController is an endpoint of the API which used for Recreations Annotated by RestController with no parameters to provide answer in application/json Annotated by RequestMapping with parameter value = "/recreation" Annotated by CrossOrigin with no parameters to give permission to connection So that RecreationController is accessed by sending requests to /recreation
